description: Lists all Add On subscriptions in your account.

nested_items.name: AddonName
nested_items.description: The name of the Add On.

nested_items.name: AddonSubscriptionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Add On subscription.

nested_items.name: AddonSubscriptionId
nested_items.description: The unique ID of the Add On subscription.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the Add On subscription was created.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If NextToken is returned, there are more results available. The value of NextToken is a unique pagination token for each page. Make the call again using the returned token to retrieve the next page.
